<p>For more information about Lavers and his life, see this <a href="https://montrealgazette.remembering.ca/obituary/gregory-lavers-1092875481" target="_blank" rel="noopener">obituary in <em>The Gazette</em></a>.</p><p>The post <a href="https://dailynous.com/2025/05/16/gregory-lavers-1974-2025/">Gregory Lavers (1974-2025)</a> first appeared on <a href="https://dailynous.com">Daily Nous</a>.</p>